cat << EOF
Net_FTP allows you to communicate with FTP
servers in a more comfortable way
than the native FTP functions of PHP do. The
class implements everything nativly
supported by PHP and additionally features like
recursive up- and downloading,
dircreation and chmodding. It although
implements an observer pattern to allow
for example the view of a progress bar.
EOF

